{"tid":2447543,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[估地區] 被控在ICU禁區性侵學妹「妳技術不錯欸！」　醫師到案說明","createTime":"2021-03-15T09:05:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T09:23:36.000Z","uid":17387,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ebe7726487aec8709559368e4178572e0e2b220a","tid":2447543,"uid":17387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:05:17.000Z","msg":"醫師被控性侵惡狼！23歲的醫學院女學生，前往北市一家醫院看診時，巧遇已在院內當主治醫師的學長，還被熱心地帶去「一個神祕的地方」，沒想到竟被帶到樓梯間性侵得逞，事後女學生PO文控訴「不想再有人受害」，還貼出三聯單說已報警控告「惡魔學長」；《蘋果新聞網》記者追查，被害人遭性侵隔天輕生被送醫，醫院知曉內情後緊急通報，被害人才在家人陪同下，勇敢向警方報案提告。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，被害女學生去年（2020年）12月28日下午3時許，獨自到該醫院就診時，利用候診空檔，她去找在該醫院放射科擔任主治醫師的學長，兩人見面敘舊後，沒想到原本欽佩的學長化身成惡魔，熱心地要帶她「一個神祕的地方」、「你肯定沒有去過」。女學生帶著仰慕之意，以為學長要帶她去參觀醫院值班室，沒想到卻是跟著學長的腳步走向一個恐怖不堪的惡夢。<br />\n<br />\n女學生PO文泣訴，原來她被帶到醫院內管制的樓梯間，學長趁無人進出時對她性侵得逞，女學生遭到痛苦折磨後，腿軟跌坐樓梯間地板，只能無助地啜泣；受害隔天，女學生想不開輕生，被家人緊急送醫，才情緒潰堤向家人哭訴遭性侵遭遇，等到身體稍微復原，即在1月2日先由醫院驗傷採證後，再由家人陪同到警局報案。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，轄區警方接獲報案後，立即依照性侵害受理程序，通知女警協助製作筆錄，也約談涉嫌性侵的醫師到案，但是該醫師向警方陳述，雙方是自願情況下發生性行為，警訊後已將此案移送地檢署偵辦。（突發中心塗豐駿／台北報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/Uf-nm1AZbKEhhxqajsHvYdsafw0=/1011x1015/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZE4E4XDOTJABJC4EMWK4LI5I3U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUf-nm1AZbKEhhxqajsHvYdsafw0%3D%2F1011x1015%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZE4E4XDOTJABJC4EMWK4LI5I3U.jpg&h=c014793a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20210315/LFJRFOPDNFGCXANQSZRR34M4VI/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2gBNg8Vo8ZBJGtMdjgDmNPIop4rOtO8avurFIa5xRVZPBoXMF-8RYKtL8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210315%2FLFJRFOPDNFGCXANQSZRR34M4VI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2gBNg8Vo8ZBJGtMdjgDmNPIop4rOtO8avurFIa5xRVZPBoXMF-8RYKtL8&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDrQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=eb775880\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210315%2FLFJRFOPDNFGCXANQSZRR34M4VI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2gBNg8Vo8ZBJGtMdjgDmNPIop4rOtO8avurFIa5xRVZPBoXMF-8RYKtL8&h=9cc437d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20210315/LFJRFOPDNFGCXANQSZRR34M4VI/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2gBNg8Vo8ZBJGtMdjgDmNPIop4rOtO8avurFIa5xRVZPBoXMF-8RYKtL8</a>"},{"pid":"9f8a2f3467bbc63dd99369ee91d1d4a396c60603","tid":2447543,"uid":17387,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:05:42.000Z","msg":"新北市又拎分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班霸"},{"pid":"4b4f287511ce35a4b768f6a55ec6ba97470ab89b","tid":2447543,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9f8a2f3467bbc63dd99369ee91d1d4a396c60603","tid":2447543,"uid":17387,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:05:42.000Z","msg":"新北市又拎分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班霸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:06:44.000Z","msg":"台北啊盲撚"},{"pid":"f31d283034316773123a78c00e51a1bc9a8fa42a","tid":2447543,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:15:05.000Z","msg":"人叻真好"},{"pid":"a6e7ad06f2089c5d73e1471428a9c9a66765b9d4","tid":2447543,"uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:16:41.000Z","msg":"女學生遭到痛苦折磨後，腿軟跌坐樓梯間地板<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n被屌到無力....<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11322cc95d8b2aedaea959bd7b20f2688cbf4ed